<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Job Posting Expiring Soon</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #F59E0B; color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 30px; background-color: #F59E0B; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .alert-box { background-color: #FEF3C7; border: 2px solid #F59E0B; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center; }
        .days-left { font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; color: #F59E0B; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>⚠️ Job Posting Expiring Soon</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi {{employerName}},</h2>
            <p>This is a friendly reminder that your job posting is expiring soon!</p>
            
            <div class="alert-box">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">{{jobTitle}}</h3>
                <p class="days-left">{{daysLeft}} days left</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>Don't let your job posting expire! Take action now to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Extend the posting duration</li>
                <li>Review and update job details</li>
                <li>Check recent applications</li>
            </ul>
            
            <a href="{{appUrl}}/employer/jobs" class="button">Manage Job Posting</a>
            
            <p>Keep your job postings active to attract the best talent!</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>The {{appName}} Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
